# Production Runbook

## Local verification

```bash
make install
make test
make run
make serve
```

Open `http://localhost:8000`.

## Scheduled run

GitHub Actions runs every 5 minutes and commits only:

```text
data/latest_report.json
web/data/signals.json
web/brief.html
```

## Failure handling

1. Check the GitHub Actions job logs.
2. Run `python scripts/run_pipeline.py --topic ai-agents --limit 8 --emit-html --log-level DEBUG`.
3. Inspect `data/latest_report.json.errors`.
4. If live RSS fails, rerun without `--live`; the seed path keeps the static site available.
5. Clear checkpoints with `aibrief clear-checkpoints` only after copying failed-run artifacts.

## Release gate

```bash
python -m compileall -q aibrief scripts cli
python -m pytest -q
python scripts/run_pipeline.py --topic "AI agents" --limit 8 --emit-html
python -m http.server 8000 -d web
```

Required HTTP checks:

```text
/                  200
/brief.html        200
/data/signals.json 200
```
